OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,FA Senedd Committee has criticised the
OL,8,FWelsh Government's approach to try and
OL,9,Fintroduce a new law to ban greyhound
OL,10,Fracing, claiming that 'confusion'
OL,11,Fstill remains over the issue and the
OL,12,Fevidence presented to it about the
OL,13,Fsport remains 'incomplete and highly
OL,14,Fcontested.'
OL,16,FMinisters in Cardiff Bay want to bring
OL,17,Fan end to the sport through the
OL,18,FProhibition of Greyhound Racing Bill.
OL,19,FIf it gets the green light, Wales will
OL,20,Fbecome the first nation in the UK to
OL,21,Fban it.
