OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,FIt comes after more than 35,000 people
OL,8,Fsigned a petition to make the sport
OL,9,Fillegal in Wales. If politicians back
OL,10,Fit, it would mean it would be an
OL,11,Foffence to operate a stadium or venue
OL,12,Fin Wales for greyhound racing and it
OL,13,Fwould be illegal to organise the sport
OL,14,Fanywhere in Wales.
OL,16,FHowever, the Senedd's Culture
OL,17,FCommittee has slammed the Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment saying it should have taken
OL,19,Fa 'more rigorous, evidence-led
OL,20,Fapproach' when introducing the
OL,21,Flegislation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/15
