OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,FIt adds it hasn't had enough time to
OL,8,Fget 'timely answers to key questions'
OL,9,Fdue to a shortened timetable which has
OL,10,Fmeant there is still confusion over
OL,11,Fthe matter.
OL,13,FThe Committee has recently published a
OL,14,Freport on the bill and says it
OL,15,Facknowledges the aim of prohibiting
OL,16,Fgreyhound racing on animal welfare
OL,17,Fgrounds, but concludes that the
OL,18,Fevidence presented to it was
OL,19,F'incomplete and highly contested.'
