OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,FThe Chair of the Committee, Delyth
OL,8,FJewell MS, says the incomplete
OL,9,Fevidence has made it more challenging
OL,10,Fto properly check the legislation.
OL,12,F"We're all agreed that animal welfare
OL,13,Fmust be the top priority in any
OL,14,Fdecision about greyhound racing, but a
OL,15,Flack of clear evidence has made the
OL,16,Fwork of scrutinising the Bill more
OL,17,Fdifficult.
