OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,F"We were asked to scrutinise a Bill
OL,8,Fwith incomplete and contested
OL,9,Fevidence, and within a shortened
OL,10,Ftimeframe. That is not how good law is
OL,11,Fmade. The Welsh Government should have
OL,12,Ftaken more time to gather robust data
OL,13,Fand consult widely."
