OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,F"The welfare of greyhounds must remain
OL,8,Fparamount. We heard serious concerns
OL,9,Fabout injuries, fatalities and
OL,10,Fsystemic welfare issues that
OL,11,Fregulation could never fully resolve.
OL,12,FAt the same time, we must acknowledge
OL,13,Fthe potential impact on those whose
OL,14,Flivelihoods depend on the sport and
OL,15,Fthis has not yet been fully assessed.
OL,17,F"The Committee believes the Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment should have taken a more
OL,19,Frigorous, evidence-led approach when
OL,20,Fintroducing legislation."
