OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,FResponding to the Committee's
OL,8,Fcriticism of the Welsh Government's
OL,9,Fapproach to the ban, Mark Bird, CEO of
OL,10,Fthe Greyhound Board of Great Britain,
OL,11,Fsaid: "The Culture Committee have
OL,12,Fcriticised every element of this Bill
OL,13,Fand how this process is being run.
OL,15,F"It is clear that they believe this
OL,16,FBill is at risk of being ill-judged
OL,17,Fand ill-considered legislation if it
OL,18,Fpassed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/15
