OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F462A1764958757
OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,F"They are as bemused and shocked as
OL,8,Feveryone else is by the political
OL,9,Fshenanigans that led to a dodgy
OL,10,Fbackroom deal becoming a dodgy Bill.
OL,11,FWe urge the Welsh government to see
OL,12,Fsense and drop this Bill in favour of
OL,13,Fregulation."
OL,15,FMeanwhile a spokesperson from the Cut
OL,16,Fthe Chase Coalition, (which comprises
OL,17,Fof Blue Cross, Dogs Trust, Greyhound
OL,18,FRescue Wales, Hope Rescue and the
OL,19,FRSPCA), has said ending greyhound
OL,20,Fracing is the only way to protect the
OL,21,Fdogs from unnecessary injury.
