OL,3,CCommittee criticises Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's handling of law to ban
OL,5,Cgreyhound racing
OL,7,F"Greyhound racing is inherently
OL,8,Fdangerous for the dogs involved.
OL,10,F"Across the UK, the industry's own
OL,11,Fdata shows that thousands of
OL,12,Fgreyhounds have been injured in recent
OL,13,Fyears as a result of racing, with
OL,14,Fhundreds having lost their lives. Such
OL,15,Frisks to dog welfare are not
OL,16,Fdefendable in the interests of sport
OL,17,For entertainment.
